cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel approach for deep learning models to learn from low-shot data stream without forgetting previous knowledge. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Among these, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories as the paper focuses on deep learning models and their application to image classification benchmarks.
